## MAMIZOU'S EXCHANGE POST
*"A fair trade is a happy trade. A clever trade is a better one."*

**Operator:** Mamizou Futatsuiwa

Facilitates item-for-item exchanges between players, NPCs, and other teams. Mamizou takes a commission and enjoys the process more than the profit.

**Core Service — Item Exchange:**
Players may trade one item for a comparable item of equivalent type and enhancement bonus.
*Example: A +1 shortsword can be exchanged for a +1 dagger of similar value.*

| Rule | Detail |
|---|---|
| Same enhancement tier required | A +1 for a +1; a +2 for a +2 |
| Processing time | 1–3 days for the replacement to arrive |
| Commission fee | 5% of the item's value (minimum 1gp) |
| Multi-party trades | Possible; Mamizou negotiates on behalf of all parties |

**Additional Services:**
- Players may sell unwanted items through her counter — she takes an 80% cut
- She can broker trades with other climber teams
- Occasionally stocks items brought in by other teams — ask what's available

**Notes:**
- She won't facilitate obviously unequal trades unless both parties knowingly consent
- She remembers everyone she's dealt with and what they traded


